[32.634049, "o", "вњ“ **HELIX evolve complete.** Kelvin conversion requirement threaded through artifact stack:\r\n\r\n**Artifacts updated (minimal, scoped changes):**\r\n1. **prd.md** вЂ” Added P0-4 and P0-5 (--to-kelvin, --from-kelvin)\r\n2. **FEAT-001** вЂ” Added FR-5, FR-6 + acceptance criteria (100В°C в†’ 373.1K, 273.15K в†’ 0В°C)\r\n3. **TD-001** вЂ” Added toKelvin/fromKelvin functions and K = C + 273.15 formula\r\n\r\n**Tracker issues created:**\r\n- `temp-converter-0ff9113c` вЂ” Add failing tests for Kelvin conversion\r\n- `temp-converter-e04c66cb` вЂ” Implement Kelvin conversion in bin/convert.js\r\n\r\nReady to proceed with build phase. Spec-to-code alignment complete.\r\n"]
